OL,3,CFour arrests after body found
OL,5,FFour people have been arrested on
OL,6,Fsuspicion of murder after the body of
OL,7,Fa woman was discovered in Milton.
OL,9,FNottinghamshire Police say officers
OL,10,Ffound the body in Main Street at
OL,11,F3.12am on Friday morning (20 March).
OL,13,FThree men, aged 37, 42, and 64, and
OL,14,Fone woman, aged 60, have been taken
OL,15,Finto police custody.
OL,17,FA police cordon is in place close to
OL,18,Fthe A1.
