OL,3,CFour arrests after body found
OL,5,FDetective Chief Inspector Ruby Burrow,
OL,6,Ffrom the East Midlands Special
OL,7,FOperations Unit, said: "We are in the
OL,8,Fearly stages of our investigation and
OL,9,Fare working to establish the
OL,10,Fcircumstances of this incident.
OL,12,F"This will impact on traffic on the A1
OL,13,Fso we apologise for any inconvenience
OL,14,Fcaused."
